      "title": "Triphasic CT Scan Abdomen at Cadabams Diagnostics | Book Today ",
      "description": "Book your CT TRIIPHASIC ABDOMEN at Cadabams Diagnostics. Same-day slots, low-dose radiation, and instant reports. Understand preparation, risks & benefits.\n",
